(1406, 20, 'content', 'This is the website to be seen on, and has the name that will be on everyone’s lips, and easy to remember and simple to recommend to others. This is definitely the most exciting, comprehensive, easy to navigate website of its kind on the internet. If you are not listed here you are not getting your fair share of the tourist business. The Accommodation, Entertainment, Restaurant and Tourism website for the 21st Century. Promoting your resort, restaurant, night club or tourist attraction here, gives you so much flexibility, more efficiency, more effectiveness, and a far more cost effective method of promoting your business than any other more expensive website or advertising medium. No commissions, charges, service or booking fees are made to either the visitor or the advertiser.\r\n\r\nThis is truly an executive website service. At a very low cost.\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;">IF YOU ARE NOT WITH US\r\nYOUR COMPETITORS ARE</h3>\r\nIt’s the holiday and tourist website that says it all, and will be remembered and talked about all over Australia, and the world. It will be used as a reference point for everyone wanting to holiday and enjoy what the South East Queensland and the Northern Rivers of NSW has to offer. Advertising on the internet can be expensive with regular annual increases but we guarantee the price you pay today, excluding introductory offers, is the price you will still be paying in 20 years’ time, even if new advertisers pay more, your rate will remain the same.\r\n\r\nYour advertisement is not stuck well down the list, but shares the top billing with-in the category with the other advertisers. Your advertisement will get its exposure at the top on a regular basis, as all the advertisements rotate/shuffle every time a visitor logs on.\r\n\r\nYour advertisements are hyperlinked directly to your website so the prospective guest can view what you have on offer together with full details of your resort/business and services. To make it even better your address and contact details are not initially available to the visitor as they will have to visit your website, giving you a better chance of getting the booking allowing you the opportunity to offer specials without entering many websites and changing details every day. It’s all done on your own website.\r\n\r\nWe do not charge any booking fees or commissions, either to you, or the visitor, allowing you to offer your best deals with your potential guest or customer. You may also advertise in as many categories as you wish and in as many locations as you wish; and tour guide operators may list their tours individually as many times as they like.\r\n<h4>ASK YOUSELF THESE QUESTIONS</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Are you getting value for money from your current website advertising?</li>\r\n 	<li>Are you paying too much to advertise on the internet?</li>\r\n 	<li>Are you getting the exposure you want?</li>\r\n 	<li>Are you getting the enquiries you want?</li>\r\n 	<li>Are you getting the clients/guests you deserve?</li>\r\n 	<li>Are you looking for a website that works and is affordable?</li>\r\n 	<li>Are you looking for a website that will be remembered by your clients/guests?</li>\r\n 	<li>Are you looking for a website that is easy to navigate and a pleasure to search through by your clients/guests, without getting bored?</li>\r\n 	<li>Do you want to be part of a website without annoying unsolicited advertisement’s and pop ups?</li>\r\n 	<li>Do you want to be a part of a website that gets the clients/guests to return time and time again?</li>\r\n 	<li>Do you want to stop paying too much for advertising on the internet?</li>\r\n 	<li>Are you sick of paying high fees and commissions to get a booking?</li>\r\n 	<li>Do you want to be on a website that really works?</li>\r\n 	<li>Are you looking for a website that is catchy, classy, professional and easy to navigate, but most of all, gets results?</li>\r\n 	<li>Do you want to be part of a website that directs potential clients/guest directly to your website free of charge?</li>\r\n 	<li>Do you want a website that caters for all tastes, that leaves the client/guests with an unforgettable experience and totally satisfied?</li>\r\n 	<li>Are you looking for a website that the clients/guests will recommend to others, and talk about?</li>\r\n 	<li>Do you want to be a part of a website that is 100% secure and safe?</li>\r\n 	<li>Would you like to be a part of the most effective and efficiency premier holiday website in Australia?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 class="blue-background" style="text-align: center;">MAKING A POSITIVE DIFFERENCE TO YOUR BUSINESS TODAY!</h4>'),
